<page>
   <topic>CLOSE_IF_EXISTS Function</topic>
   <syntax>N close_if_exists(C name )</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>name</name>
         <description>The name of a layout.
</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Public user defined function.</description>
   <discussion>
The CLOSE_IF_EXISTS() function closes a layout if it is open. This function will also close reports when in design mode.
Limitations: Desktop applications only.
   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
dim ptr as P
ptr = form.view("Customer Information")
? close_if_exists("Customer Information")
]]></example>
   
